trans-unit.source: Represents the <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> usado na criptografia XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class represents the `<ReferenceList>` element of an encrypted document XML signature defined by the XML encryption specification.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> classe representa o `<ReferenceList>` elemento de uma assinatura XML do documento criptografado definida pela especificação de criptografia de XML.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class contains references to <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements that were encrypted by a key contained within another <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> classe contém referências a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementos que foram criptografados por uma chave contida dentro de outra <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class uses <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elements, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> classe usa <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elementos façam referência ao <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elementos, e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elementos façam referência ao <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementos.

trans-unit.source: You can add only <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objects to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> collection.
trans-unit.target: Você pode adicionar apenas <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> ou <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objetos para o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> coleção.

trans-unit.source: For more information about XML encryption standards, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre os padrões de criptografia de XML, consulte http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
